About the Store

Your Canadian online source for adhesvie vinyls (Oracal 651 & 631, Styletech), Siser Heat Transfer Vinyl, patterned HTV and adhesive vinyls.  We also offer various blanks (clothing, sublimation etc.)

Our goal is to offer crafters and small businesses the full spectrum of colours and size options, amazing prices and service beyond your expectations.
